1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about evidence hierarchy than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,400
In science, we rank evidence from strongest to weakest.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,800
But online, it’s a wild west.

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,000
At the top?

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,200
Randomized controlled trials.

6
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:13,600
Bottom?

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,800
Anecdotes and opinions.

8
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:17,200
This hierarchy helps us gauge reliability.

9
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:19,600
Without it, misinformation spreads like wildfire.

10
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:24,400
Understanding this can empower you to make informed choices and avoid pitfalls.

11
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:27,200
Want to learn more about evidence-based thinking?

12
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,800
Hit that follow button!
